* Offline-first architecture.
* Single-user application in Phase 1.
* Future multi-user support must not be blocked by current decisions.
* Arabic is the primary language.
* RTL support is mandatory.
* Headings use "قمرة" font.
* Body text uses "Alyamama" font.
* Follow existing project structure.
* Do not rename files, folders, routes, providers or models unless explicitly requested.
* Do not change business logic without explaining why.
* When fixing a bug, prefer minimal targeted changes.
* Always inspect related Providers, Services and Routing before modifying UI code.
* Never generate placeholder implementations.
* Never leave TODO comments as final solutions.
* Production-quality code only.
